This Resource list the available power sources for the Device. The
Property "powersources" is a list that is read only and is
informative only. If there is more than 1 power source active, use
multiple Resources to indicate the active power sources. If the power
source is unknown use the value "unknown".
Fault detected in currently active power source. True = fault
